de.mpa.algorithms.fragmentation

Interface Ion

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FragmentIon

    public interface Ion
    This class represents an Ion object. It holds the ion number, the ion score and the 6 different types of ions: 1) a-c ions 2) x-z ions
    Author:
    Thilo Muth
